title: Another Worlds. From Lithuania to Disneyland Paris 2013. Full jo
description:
This film is a realistic documentary about the journey from Lithuania to Disneyland Resort Paris and how the reality changes after crossing of various borders - in the real world and Disneyland Paris world, in the past and present... The film displays what the traveler sees and feels during such a trip. Subtitles and QR codes (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Qr_code) are used instead of voice narration and provides interesting information about scenery of this film.

Recommended to watch full screen, 1080p. 720p files are also included for those, who have slow computers. You can download 1 min 36 s test files to compare 1080p and 720p quality. There are photos extracted from the film in the folder 'nuotraukos'.
